{"tid":258232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬逢國：倡「復活節星期一」同日　改作「孔聖誕日」假","createTime":"2017-05-26T02:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T08:03:23.000Z","uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0168d47ea4e9b7ad5eb217dab12df7af80f41761","tid":258232,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"體育、演藝、文化及出版界立法會議員馬逢國早前向政府提出建議，希望每年的公眾假期增訂「孔聖誕日」，同時刪減「復活節星期一」假期，受到關注。他今日在《都市日報》專欄撰文指出，建議並非刪去4月「復活節星期一」的假期，而是將該日改為「孔聖誕日」，稱「絕無中斷各打工仔長假的意思」，實際上不改變現有公眾假期安排。<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國指出，孔教領袖們在提倡增設「孔聖誕日」的時候，也希望盡量減低市民的影響，經與其他五大宗教領袖商議後，大家均同意上述的安排。孔教的朋友也曾去信政府要求考慮有關建議，可惜未見回音。<br />\n<br />\n專欄提到，孔教的朋友希望在公眾假期中撥出一天，以紀念孔聖先師，「藉此推動儒家思想，喚起社會對傳統中華文化價值的關注和重視，訴求也是合理。」<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國早前向政府提問指，鑑於有孔教領袖建議每年的公眾假期增訂「孔聖誕日」，並刪減「復活節星期一」，以維持每年的公眾假期總日數不變，問及當局會否考慮建議。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長蕭偉強以書面回覆指，有關訂立「孔聖誕日」為公眾假期並刪減「復活節星期一」的建議，「至今未見有社會廣泛的訴求」，故須小心處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B7%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E9%95%B7%E5%81%87-%E9%A6%AC%E9%80%A2%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BE%A9%E6%B4%BB%E7%AF%80%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%80-%E5%90%8C%E6%97%A5-%E6%94%B9%E4%BD%9C-%E5%AD%94%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%97%A5-%E5%81%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2581%2587-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2580%25A2%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25B8%2580-%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%2594%25B9%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E5%25AD%2594%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%2581%2587%2F&d=JOznHiMcqeBMxdp32aSgwzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=574fba2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2581%2587-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2580%25A2%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%25E4%25B8%2580-%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%2594%25B9%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E5%25AD%2594%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%2581%2587%2F&h=ffebbc28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B7%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E9%95%B7%E5%81%87-%E9%A6%AC%E9%80%A2%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BE%A9%E6%B4%BB%E7%AF%80%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E4%B8%80-%E5%90%8C%E6%97%A5-%E6%94%B9%E4%BD%9C-%E5%AD%94%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%97%A5-%E5%81%87/</a>"},{"pid":"e1840a9d4933727e3ef397a65f5c3e0e185525fe","tid":258232,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"真係腦殘 你話加一日假咪全城叫好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55932b0b671c526ccf9cef5e1e01431dcb059fd6","tid":258232,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"放多一日假都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524530dce5c4f0238d9ac29aa30b68b3317c8110","tid":258232,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:22:31.000Z","msg":"加埋毛魔節丫嘛"},{"pid":"f1f56f40a2a32dcfc1576150a1896e05f4e3578d","tid":258232,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"耶教vs支那，連登/高登仔會反邊個多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244f91cbc57deed5d889f9bf162a6b9696b0796b","tid":258232,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T02:36:48.000Z","msg":"柒碌 老西都唔能轉<br />\n一震轉能左名 遲下連西方假都無鳩埋<br />\n跟埋大陸 佢老味都on99<br />\n家震啲高官 講呢啲野出黎之前有無諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3205ff85c4de4